name: DogGroomers.com
overview:
DogGroomers.com is a website that connects dog owners with local dog grooming services in the United States.

Visitors to DogGroomers.com can search for a dog groomer using their city, neighborhood, or zip code, and they will find dog groomers that have signed up in those areas.

Dog groomers are able to add important information about their business, including contact information, location, services offered, pricing, and other descriptive information about its company. A contact form allows dog owners to directly contact each dog groomer to book appointments, check pricing, or learn more about the company. Groomers may also add special offers and incentives to track visitors and referrals from the website.

DogGroomers.com serves a niche market of dog grooming professionals from around the United States, and the website makes it easy for dog owners to find local dog grooming companies.

The site is currently seeking relationships with complimentary companies in the dog supply, pet care, pet deals, and dog information verticals.
